Last updated: March 2026

Days Calculator is an Android application designed to help users calculate the number of remaining office and remote work days required to meet quarterly work balance requirements.

The application was created primarily for employees of Getinge whose employment contracts require them to complete approximately 40% of their working days from the office and 60% remotely within each quarter.

Data Collection

Days Calculator does not collect, store, process, or transmit any personal data.

The application does not require user accounts, registration, or login.

Data Storage

All calculations performed by the application are executed locally on the user's device.
The application does not send any information to external servers.

Third-Party Services

Days Calculator does not use third-party services, analytics tools, advertising networks, or external data processing systems.

Internet Access

The application does not require internet access for its functionality.

Data Sharing

Because the application does not collect or store user data, no data is shared with the developer or any third parties.

Intended Use

The application is intended to assist users in calculating the number of remaining office and remote working days needed to achieve the correct work distribution by the end of a quarterly period.

